ISLAMABAD, Jan 17 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib on Monday asked the PML-N president Shehbaz Sharif to explain his relations with Masroor Anwar, who “used to collect money and deposit it in his accounts.”
In a tweet, he said Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) President who claimed to be an honest man should dare to speak about his ‘cash boy’ Masroor Anwar.
